description: Borinquen [Borikén] was the original name given to the Island of Puerto Rico by one of its original inhabitants the indigenous Taino Warriors. Borinquen [Borikén] translates to “Land of the Valiant and Noble Lord.” The goal of Borinquen Soul is to showcase the love and orgullo these guys have for their vibrant culture through the authenticity and quality of their flavorful comida. Their mission? To provide the diverse communities of the Bay Area with a "Taste of Puerto Rico" while reconnecting the home-sick Boricuas with the comida criolla they miss dearly. Check out this fantastic truck on the streets of the Bay Area today!
name: Borinquen Soul
